## Polyglot Makefiles: Working with Foreign Languages
<hr style="width:100%;border-bottom:3px solid black;">

This section collects several demos of working with foreign languages.  Polyglots in `compose.mk` are roughly comparable to [justfile shebang recipes](https://github.com/casey/just?tab=readme-ov-file#shebang-recipes). Because `compose.mk` also adds native-ish support for docker, [including inlined Dockerfiles]({{mkdocs.site_relative_url}}/raw-docker), you can also super-charge our polyglots with *arbitrary containerized interpretters*, with or without customizing stock images.

Polyglots come in a few basic types, and this page tries to cover the main categories, but there's an index of [more involved examples](#other-examples) at the end.

